...

Total: 42 bullets (3 proven, 15 accepted, 24 candidates)
```

Sorting:
- Default: by score (descending)
- Can add --sort option later (by category, maturity, created, etc)

Column widths:
- ID: 12 chars
- Category: 20 chars
- Maturity: 12 chars
- Score: 8 chars
- Content: remaining width (truncate with ellipsis if needed)

